search_results.title: About
search_results.snippet: Boston Dynamics is the global leader in developing and deploying highly mobile robots capable of tackling industry's toughest challenges.

search_results.title: Boston Dynamics
search_results.snippet: Boston Dynamics, Inc., is an American engineering and robotics design company founded in 1992 as a spin-off from the Massachusetts Institute of Technology.

search_results.title: Marc Raibert | Keynote Speaker
search_results.snippet: Marc Raibert is the founder and former CEO and president of Boston Dynamics, a company recognized for developing advanced robots that mimic animal movement.
